<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Erwirdiger und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt
                        Conrad Prünster der elter, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, wie daz der
                        Lucz von Veltprech, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> armman, seinen arnman von
                        Viczenczenprunne, der Smidfricze <expan>gena<ex>n</ex>t</expan>, mitsampte
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> weib und kinden gen Wirczburg auf
                        geistlich gerihte von werltlicher sache wegen geladen hab und er doch dem
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>, von dem seinen vormals nie khein reht
                        darümb <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan> hab. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> daran weisen wöllet, daz er von der klag
                        lasse, das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. Und het
                            <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ders<ex>elbe</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> armman czu dem
                        <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> armman, icht
                            <expan>czusprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wil
                        im <expan>ders<ex>elbe</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> von <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogens</expan>
                        sleunigs <expan>reht<ex>en</ex></expan> gern helffen,
                            <expan>wen<ex>n</ex></expan> er des ermandt wirdt.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> diem
                                <expan>palma<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
